Francois Belleau presents the different aspects of Linked Data and answer th following questions :

 * What is Linked Data ?
 * What is a Triple ?
 * What is RDF ?
 * What is SPARQL query language ?

These are the links used during the presentation :

http://delicious.com/fbelleau/bh2010:primer

You can also follow this tutorial to play with RDF and SPARQL:

   http://www.semantic-systems-biology.org/biogateway/tutorial
